      <title>Ozempic 潜在致盲关联促使监管机构寻求调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/ozempic-blinding-link-potential-prompts-regulator-to-seek-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦药品管理局表示，将要求欧洲当局审查两项新研究，这两项研究指出，诺和诺德公司的重磅药物 Ozempic 与一种罕见的视力丧失之间存在联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/ozempic-blinding-link-potential-prompts-regulator-to-seek-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 10:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
